operty acquisition, development, and litigation.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Litigation</h3>\n                    <p>Aggressive and strategic representation in civil and commercial disputes.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Intellectual Property</h3>\n                    <p>Protecting your innovations and brand with robust IP strategies.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <div class=\"contact-item\">\n                    <h3>Contact Us</h3>\n                    <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Legal Way, Suite 100, Justice City, JC 54321</p>\n                    <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href=\"tel:+15551234567\">(555) 123-4567</a></p>\n                    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:info@apexlegal.com\">info@apexlegal.com</a></p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"contact-item\">\n                    <h3>Office Hours</h3>\n                    <p>Monday - Friday: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM</p>\n                    <p>Saturday & Sunday: By Appointment Only</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Legal Group. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}